# MongoDB Atlas Connection String
# Uncomment and set your MongoDB Atlas connection string here
# The connection string format: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/database?appName=AppName
# MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/database?appName=AppName

# IMPORTANT: If you're getting connection errors, make sure:
# 1. Your IP address is whitelisted in MongoDB Atlas Network Access
# 2. Visit: https://cloud.mongodb.com/v2#/security/network/list
# 3. Add your current IP or use 0.0.0.0/0 for development (less secure)
# 4. The server will automatically display your current IP when connection fails